This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with generating images from text input. It also involves the use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) which is a popular technique in computer vision. 

The paper also involves the use of a captioning network to caption on generated images, which falls under the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). 

The use of GANs and captioning networks also involves machine learning techniques, which falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). 

Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of the proposed method through extensive comparisons with existing methods, which falls under the sub-category of Graphics (cs.GR).
